<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>FAQ | Southern Love Kitchen</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="faq-page container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
          <p>We accept cash, credit/debit cards, Zelle, and Cash App. Online payments coming soon!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you deliver?</h3>
          <p>Yes, we offer local delivery in the Alexandria area. Delivery fees may apply depending on your location.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Are your dishes gluten-free or vegan?</h3>
          <p>Many of our dishes can be made gluten-free or vegan. Check our menu for dietary labels or ask when you order!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do I book catering?</h3>
          <p>Use our <a href="catering.html">Catering & Events</a> page to send an inquiry, or call/email us to discuss your needs!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I order for a large group?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely! We love feeding a crowd. Please contact us for custom quotes for big orders or events.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you have gift cards?</h3>
          <p>Gift cards will be available soon! Stay tuned for updates.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="scripts/auth.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
